<author>nạdr sẖwqy</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿbrt bnạ wdʿwtnạ ạly̱ rḥlẗ mjd wrạỷk ldẖạ nsẖdw ḥbạaⁿ lk dkẖlt bnạ ạly̱ ʿhdk gẖsltnạ wmsḥtnạ ldẖạ nʿln mjdạaⁿ llk ạ̉nt tṭlq zmn ạntṣạr nḥn nʿln sẖʿbk ymsẖy̱ wrạỷk nʿln mʿk hạtfyn kl ḍʿf yạ̉ty̱ bạmtlạk nlbs ạlsmạʾ nsqṭ ʿnạ ṭạrḥyn kl tẖwb bạl rmạd nkẖṭw llạ̉mjạd ạ̉nt tṭlq mjd wbhạʾ nḥn nʿln sẖʿbk ymsẖy̱ wrạỷk njry̱ mʿk ʿạbryn nʿln qwẗ dẖlk ạ̉ntṣạr tsẖʿlnạ bnạr nhtf mʿk frḥyn ndkẖl mʿk ạ̉rḍ ạlạ̉mtlạk nʿln gẖnạk</lyrics>
<title>ʿbrt bnạ</title>
</song>